ogyparis/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eInstagram\u003c/a\u003e / \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@typologyparis\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTikTok\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat: \u003c/strong\u003eA Parisian \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin-care\u003c/a\u003e brand offering serums, moisturizers, eye creams, sun care and a line of tinted products (lip oils, brow gel, concealer, mascara and more) for less than $60.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice Range: \u003c/strong\u003e$21 - $59\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFounder:\u003c/strong\u003e Ning Li\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrigin Story:\u003c/strong\u003e Founded in 2019, Typology is a French skin-care brand dedicated to creating effective, transparent and \u0026#34;eco-friendly\u0026#34; products. The brand focuses on minimalist formulations using high-quality, natural ingredients and offers a wide range of skin-care solutions from serums to cleansers. Typology is known for its innovative approach, leveraging scientific research to develop products that cater to individual skin concerns without unnecessary additives. Its commitment to \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/sustainability\"\u003esustainability\u003c/a\u003e is reflected in its \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/2019/04/ethical-fashion-certification-list\"\u003eB Corp\u003c/a\u003e certification, \u0026#34;eco-conscious\u0026#34; packaging and direct-to-consumer model.\u003c/p\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003cp\u003eTypology distinguishes itself by using a limited number of natural ingredients, prioritizing sustainability and transparency. Its products are designed to be simple yet effective, avoiding unnecessary additives. Each product is cruelty-free, vegan and tailored for a range of skin types, aiming for a clean, straightforward approach to \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/skin-care\"\u003eskin care\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/ImageObject\"\u003e\u003cphoenix-picture\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, calc(33vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_127/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.webp 127w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_207/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.webp 207w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_234/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.webp 234w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_414/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.webp 414w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_467/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.webp 467w\"/\u003e\u003csource sizes=\"(min-width: 1600px) 1600px, calc(33vw - 40px)\" data-srcset=\"https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_127/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.jpg 127w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_207/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.jpg 207w, https://fashionista.com/.image/ar_100:143%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_234/MjExMjEwMjkyNjExMjYyNDIz/typology-black-cherry-tinted-lip-oil.jpg